          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-1" n="1">A Bard on whom Phoebus his Spirit bestow'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-2" n="2">Resolv'd to acknowledge the bounty he ow'd,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-3" n="3">Found out a new method at once of confessing,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-4" n="4">And making the most of so mighty a blessing.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-5" n="5">To the God he'd be grateful, but Mortals he'd chouse,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-6" n="6">By making his Patron preside in his house;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-7" n="7">And wisely foresaw this advantage from thence,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-8" n="8">That the God must in honour bear most of th'expense.</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-9" n="9">So the Bard he finds Drink, and leaves Phoebus to treat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-10" n="10">With the Thoughts he inspires, regardless of Meat;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-11" n="11">Hence they that come hither expecting to dine,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-262-501A-line-12" n="12">Are always fob\<hi rend="italics">add</hi>Â·b\'d off with sheer wit, &amp; sheer Wine.</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
